		(at 17.54 108.54 180)
		(descr "Samtec MCX-J-P-H-ST-TH1, 50 ohm MCX jack, straight (vertical), through-hole. Recommended PCB layout per Samtec drawing MCX-J-P-X-ST-TH1 rev D: 4x ground posts drill 1.40 on a 5.08x5.08 square + center signal drill 1.10. Cable mates straight up (off the board face). Body sq 6.0 mm; mating barrel 4.50 mm. Signal pin plated through all layers -> QSE B.Cu escape lands on it with no face-change via.")
